content: Beyond the wall, you can find a thin ledge leading along the rocky cave wall guarded by a Dragonfly Guai peppering you with poison arrows. After you cross the gap, you can spot torches up the wall on the right, and a lower path to the left leading back down to an overlook for the Upper Hollow Shrine, complete with a green Wisp to absorb along the ledge.
